      "column": "left",
      "text": "To Spaiditu/to Eadan-\nsitu / jeb Saplohsfitu / jeb israh-\nmitu junis ne buhs tam KUN-\nGAM uppureht / to junis fawa\nSemmê ne buhs darriht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jums arri ne buhs no ta\nSwefchineeka Rohkas / juhfam\nDeewam no wiſfahm Schahm Lee-\ntahm ne kahdu Barribu uppu-\nreht/jo tahs Leeti ne derr/ tahm irr\nWaina / tahs ne buhs no junis\nlabbi patihkamas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGSrunnaja\nus Mohsu/un fazzija :\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad kahds Wehrfis / jeb\nYehrs / jeb Kaslens dsemm / tad\nbuhs tam feptinas Deenas pee\nfawas Mahtes palikt / bet astota\nDeenâ un pehz buhs tas patih-\nkains / par Ugguni tam KUR-\nGAM.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jums arri ne buhs weenu\nleetu Lohpu jeb Avi/lihds ar fawu\nAngli weenâ Deenâ nokant.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad juhs weenu Teik-\nschanas-Uppuri tam KUNGAM\nuppurefeet/ tad buhs junis to up-\npureht/ka tas no junis patihkains.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tai paſchâ Deenâ buhs\nto ehft / junis ne buhs no ta lihds\nRihtam atlizzinaht/ Es efinu tas\nKUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nu buhs junis mannis\nBaustus turreht / un tohs dar-\nriht/ es efinu tas KUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un junis ne buhs mannis\nfwehtu Wahrdiu pulgoht / ka es\nIsraêta Behrau Starpâ sweh-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas Es juhs no Egiptes-\nSeminês iſweddïs eſmu / ka es\njums var Deewu buhtu / Es tas\nKUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ehz to runnaja tas\nKUNGS us Mohsu /\nun fazzija :\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Runna us Israêka Behr-\nneem/un fakkins teemi: ta KUN-\nGA Swehtkeim / ko jums buhs\nisfaukt / buhs fivehtahm Safank-\nschanahm buht / khee irr manni\nSwehtki.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Seſchas Deenas buhs to\nDarbu darriht / bet feptita Deena\nirr ta leela Duffeschanas-Deena/\nweena fwehta Safaukschana / ne\nkahdu Darbu buhs jums darriht/\nta irr ta KUNGA Duffeschanas-\nDeena wiſſds juhfds Dsihwokrôs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schee irr ta KUNGA no-\nlikti Swehtki/ tahs fivehtas Sa-\nfaukschanas/ko jums buhs isfaukt\nfawâ nosazzitâ Laika.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pirma Mehneti zettortâ\npadesinitâ Mehnes Deenâ / ap\nWakkara Laiku/ irr ta KUNGA\nPaſta-Swehtki.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un peektâpadesinitâ Deenâ\ntai paſchâ Mehneti / irr to nerau-\ndsetu Maisu Swehtki ta KUN-\nGA/\n"
    }
  ],
